data.text: Goodou heia godou danggee gi Dimaadua, haga dele ina ono maaloo.
Daahili hagaamuina Dimaadua.
Gidaadou gi hagalaamua di ingoo dabu o Maa.
Hula gi Dimaadua, e kae ai godou hagamaamaa,
Goodou ala go di hagadili o Abraham, go dana dangada hai hegau,
Mee go Dimaadua go tadau God.
Mee ga dadaahi hua beelaa dana hagababa gaa hana hua beelaa,
Mee ga dadaahi hua di hagababa dela ne hai go Mee gi Abraham
Dimaadua la guu hai dana hagababa gi Jacob,
Mee ne helekai, “Au ga gowadu gi di goe tenua go Canaan, e hai tenua ni aau.”105.11 Genesis 28.13
Nia daangada a God la nogo hogoohi, nogo noho i Canaan be digau henua gee.
Digaula nogo tataele i mehanga nia henua, i mehanga tenua nei mo tenua nei.
Malaa, Dimaadua la hagalee hai digaula gii hai hagahuaidu go tangada,
ga helekai, “Goodou hudee hagahuaidu ina agu gau hai hegau ne hilihili aanei.
Dimaadua e hagau mai dana dau magamaga gi nia henua digaula,
Gei Mee ga hagau dana daane i mua digaula,
Nia wae o maa guu nnoo gi nia daula baalanga,
gaa dae loo gi di kila aga o ana kokohp ala ne hai.
Di king o Egypt gu daa gi daha a Joseph mo di hale galabudi,
ga haga menege aga a mee gaa dagi dono hale mo e dagi dono henua hagatau.105.21 Genesis 41.39-41
Mee gu aamua i hongo nia dagi huogodoo a di king,
Malaa, Jacob guu hana gi Egypt guu noho i tenua deelaa,105.23 Genesis 46.6; 47.11
Dimaadua guu hai digaula gi dogologowaahee,
Mee guu hai digau Egypt gi hagadugina e ginaadou i ana daangada
Malaa, Dimaadua gu hagau ana daangada hai hegau
Meemaa guu hai nia hegau maaloo dangihi a God,
Dimaadua guu hai tenua deelaa gi bouli dongoeho,
Mee guu huli nia wai o nia monowai digaula gii hai nia dodo,
Tenua digaula guu honu kailuu, mo i lodo hogi di hale o di king.105.30 Exodus 8.1-6
God ne helekai hua, gei nia hagabae lamu
Mee ne hagau ia dana uwa hadu magalillili mo nia ila
Mee ne hunahuna nia laagau ‘grape’ mo nia laagau ‘fig’ digaula,
Mee ne helekai hua gei nia ‘locust’ gu lloomoi,
Digaula guu gai nia laagau huogodoo o tenua deelaa, mo nia huwa laagau.105.35 Exodus 10.12-15
Mee gu daaligi nia ulu mmaadua dama daane
Gei mee ne dagi mai digau Israel gi daha mo Egypt,
Digau Egypt gu tenetene gi digaula ala ne hula,
Dimaadua e holo dana gololangi gi hongo digaula,
Digaula ne dangi gi Mee,
Mee ne huge di hadugalaa, gei nia wai gu malingi mai,
Mee e langalangahia hua igolo dana hagababa haga madagu
Malaa, Mee guu lahi ana daangada ala ne hilihili la gi daha,
Mee guu wanga gi digaula nia henua o digau ala i golo,
bolo digaula gi hagalongo gi ana haganoho,
